  (173, 'matthew_luxton_personal_standing_order', 'MATTHEW LUXTON', NULL, '<', 0, ARRAY[3]::int[], 'personal_spend', 0.75, 'panel 2026-07-10, verified CONFIRMED; 21 rows, exact -£255.00 every month via Faster Payment standing order on Jo''s personal account (6), unbroken 2023-10-04 to 2025-06-04. No supplier/business narrative anywhere in the description (just name + FP timestamp), no counterparty registry match for Luxton. Same evidentiary shape as the existing precedent rule id 105 for MISS C A COLLINGS (regular fixed'),
  (174, 'eon_next_household_energy_dd', 'E\.ON NEXT', NULL, '<', 0, ARRAY[3,4]::int[], 'direct_debit', 0.85, 'panel 2026-07-10, verified CONFIRMED; Household energy supplier direct debits on Jo''s personal current account (6) and the Joint Account (10), 2025-04-28 to 2026-05-28, all debits, amounts step in plausible seasonal/tariff-review bands per account (£72-109 on acct 6, £222-343 on acct 10) consistent with two separate metered supplies billed monthly. No existing rule catches E.ON: rules 33/34 only a'),
  (175, 'gocardless_tamarkoffi_business_dd', 'TAMARKOFFI-BEMEM67', NULL, '<', 0, ARRAY[1]::int[], 'direct_debit', 0.70, 'panel 2026-07-10, verified CONFIRMED; 26+ GoCardless-collected direct debits on the pub trading account (15), 2024-07-09 to 2025-12-19, all debits, variable amounts (£106-428) consistent with a usage-based service/subscription fee rather than a fixed rent-style payment. Existing rule id 37 (priority 45, ''^GOCARDLESS'') is anchored to the start of the description and misses these because the actual '),
  (176, 'Mobile — O2 (bare, no trailing token)', '^O2$', NULL, '<', 0, ARRAY[3]::int[], 'direct_debit', 0.95, 'panel 2026-07-10, verified CONFIRMED; Existing rule 45 ''Mobile — O2'' requires ''^O2 '' (trailing space) and misses the bare 2-char description ''O2'' used in this feed''s format. 38 rows, all account 6 (Jo personal current), all negative, consistent -£17 to -£55 monthly mobile bill cadence 2019-2026.'),
