  (182, 'ATM cash withdrawal (BMACH)', '^BMACH', NULL, '<', 0, ARRAY[3]::int[], 'personal_spend', 0.88, 'panel 2026-07-10, verified CONFIRMED; No existing rule; 100% of BMACH rows are needs_review. Account 6 only, 4 cash-machine withdrawals 2019-2020, all negative round amounts (£40-£200) typical of personal ATM cash.'),
